What this license covers
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The CC BY 4.0 license covers this work's original contribution:

  - the maturity leveling — the sequencing of guardrail controls across
    Levels 1 through 4;
  - the consolidation of overlapping industry guidance into a single,
    non-redundant catalog of controls;
  - the AI-specificity discipline that distinguishes a genuine AI guardrail
    from general security practice; and
  - the prose, structure, and cross-linking written for this repository.

